   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Scholar's Shield</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img title="Scholar's Shield" src="/file/Elden-Ring/scholars_shield-elden-ring-wiki-guide-200px.png" alt="scholars shield elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Glintstone Sorceries" href="/Glintstone+Sorceries" target="">Glintstone Sorceries</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost&nbsp;30</td> 
     <td>Slots Used&nbsp;1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Enhances left-handed shield damage negation 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Int 12 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Scholar's Shield</strong> is a&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sorceries" href="/Sorceries" target="">Sorcery</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Scholar's Shield spell</strong>&nbsp;boosts the defensive capabilities of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Shields" href="/Shields" target="">Shield</a>&nbsp;players equip on their left hand.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>One of the glintstone sorceries of the Academy of Raya Lucaria.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Enchants shield held in the left hand with additional damage negation.<br>This sorcery can be cast while in motion.<br></em></p> 
 <p><em>Taught to the Knights of the Cuckoo by the academy as payment for their contract.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Scholar's Shield</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Scholar's Shield</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Can be purchased from&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sorceress Sellen" href="/Sorceress+Sellen" target="">Sorceress Sellen</a>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<img title="Runes" src="/file/Elden-Ring/runes-currency-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="runes currency elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18"> 2,500&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Runes" href="/Runes" target="">Runes</a>. Sellen is located in&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Limgrave" href="/Limgrave" target="">Limgrave</a>:&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Waypoint Ruins" href="/Waypoint+Ruins" target="">Waypoint Ruins</a>.&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=707&amp;lat=-193.125&amp;lng=112.885645&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=707&amp;lat=-193.125&amp;lng=112.885645&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>..</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Scholar's Shield Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Glintstone Sorceries" href="/Glintstone+Sorceries">Glintstone Sorcery</a></li> 
 <li>Cast this spell with a staff in your right hand, whilst a shield is equipped in your left hand.</li> 
 <li>Lasts 1 minute (60 seconds). 
  <ul> 
   <li>&nbsp;With <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Old Lord's Talisman" href="/Old+Lord's+Talisman">Old Lord's Talisman</a> equipped, this duration becomes 1:18 minutes (78 seconds)</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
 <li>Guard Boost +25%</li> 
 <li>Guarded Damage Negation +30% 
  <ul> 
   <li>Magic Guarded Damage Negation +70%</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
